show.title: In search of jade

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/p2mnK6
show.description: Jade finds herself trapped between a ruthless tycoon and a ruthless gang leader—both hunting a hard drive that could destroy Interpol. In a deadly game of power and survival, she must rely on her wits, instincts, and every skill she has. A high-octane thriller where trust is a gamble and only the smartest will stay alive.
